snippet.title: Poison Control - Character Trailer (Nintendo Switch, PS4) (EU - English)
snippet.description:
Learn more @ https://nisamerica.com/poison-control

You'll never know who you'll run into in Poison Control! And as you'll quickly discover, the denizens of Hell each have their own story to tell. What twisted tales will you unveil?

Coming 16 April 2021 to Nintendo Switch and PS4.

#PoisonControlGame #NISAmerica
